metadata.name: MegaKurs Monsters #1
metadata.description:
NFT collection MegaKurs Monsters was released to honour the 1st edition of the MegaKurs. I am one of the students from Samurai School, who reach the final stage of the course.
I would like to give a big shout-out to Kuba and Bartek, who are sharing their knowledge and delivering the best atmosphere during the challange.Mega Kurs Monsters collection was created to honour all participants in mention advanture. That was real pleasure to go through with you. Try to catch monster which traits really represent YOU! 
My message to adepts of Samurai Coding School: Do not give up and keep learning!
